            <h1 style="font-family: Arial Hebrew, Arial; direction: rtl; padding-left: 2.5em; padding-right: 2em; font-size: 2.6em;">
               אסותא - תור לבדיקה
            </h1>
            <p style="font-family: Arial Hebrew, Arial; direction: rtl; padding-left: 2.5em; padding-right: 3.7em; font-size: 2em; line-height: 1.6em;">
שלום {!Appointment__c.Patient_Account__c},
<br>
להלן פרטי הבדיקה שנקבעה עבורך:
<br>
<br>
<b>אתר :</b> {!Appointment__c.Site__c}
<br>
<b>תאריך:</b> {!Appointment__c.Date_of_appointment__c}
<br>
<b>שעה:</b> {!Appointment__c.AppointmentTime__c}
<br>
<b>מידע עבור התור:</b> נא ללחוץ <a href={!Appointment__c.kit_for_inst__c}>כאן</a> 
<br>
{!Appointment__c.link_memo_text__c}
<br>
<p style="font-family: Arial Hebrew, Arial; direction: rtl; padding-left: 2.5em; padding-right: 3.7em; font-size: 2em; line-height: 1.6em;">{!IF( Appointment__c.Site_Code__c = "33" ,"חדש! כל השירותים בלחיצת כפתור: https://bit.ly/2SGz4KW","")}</p>
<br>
<p style="font-family: Arial Hebrew, Arial; direction: rtl; padding-left: 2.5em; padding-right: 3.7em; font-size: 2em; line-height: 1.6em;">
בברכה,
<br>
אסותא
</p>
